Minor: Information Sciences and Technology in Health Policy and Administration Minor
Program_Policies: A grade of C or better is required for all courses in the minor, as specified by Senate Policy 59-10. In addition, at least six credits of the minor must be unique from the prescribed courses required by a student's major(s).; Note: The HPA courses have additional prerequisites that must be met.
